                            32. 3 ton + 500 ons + 100 kg = . . . gr​</h2><br />
                        <p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>3 ton + 500 ons + 100 kg = . . . . gram</p><p><strong>P</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>y</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>l</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>s</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong> </strong><strong>:</strong></p><p>Mula-Mula, kita jadikan Gram terlebih dahulu.</p><p>3 ton = 3.000.000 Gram.</p><p>500 ons = 14174,762 Gram.</p><p>100 kg = 100.000 Gram.</p><p>Tinggal di tambahkan semua.</p><p>= 3.000.000 + 14174,762 + 100.000 = 17.274.762</p><p><strong>J</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>d</strong><strong>i</strong><strong> </strong><strong>H</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>s</strong><strong>i</strong><strong>l</strong><strong> </strong><strong>D</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>r</strong><strong>i</strong><strong> </strong><strong>3</strong><strong> </strong><strong>T</strong><strong>o</strong><strong>n</strong><strong> </strong><strong>+</strong><strong> </strong><strong>5</strong><strong>0</strong><strong>0</strong><strong> </strong><strong>O</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>s</strong><strong> </strong><strong>+</strong><strong> </strong><strong>1</strong><strong>0</strong><strong>0</strong><strong> </strong><strong>K</strong><strong>g</strong><strong> </strong><strong>=</strong><strong> </strong><strong>1</strong><strong>7</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>2</strong><strong>7</strong><strong>4</strong><strong>.</strong><strong>7</strong><strong>6</strong><strong>2</strong><strong> </strong><strong>G</strong><strong>r</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>.</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>#</strong><strong>S</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>o</strong><strong>g</strong><strong>a</strong><strong> </strong><strong>M</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>b</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>t</strong><strong>u</strong><strong>.</strong></p><p>Tetap <strong>S</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>m</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>n</strong><strong>g</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>t</strong><strong> </strong><strong>B</strong><strong>e</strong><strong>l</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>j</strong><strong>a</strong><strong>r</strong><strong>.</strong></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>Jawaban:</strong></p><p>3 ton + 500 ons + 100 kg = </p><p><strong>Penjelasan dengan langkah-langkah:</strong></p><p>1 ton = 1.000.000 gr</p><p>1 ons = 100 gr</p><p>1 kg = 1000 gr</p><p>jadi, </p><p>1.000.000 x 3 (ton) = 3.000.000 gr</p><p>100 x 500 (ons) = 50.000 gr</p><p>1000 x 100 (kg) = 100.000 gr</p><p>jadi 3.000.000 + 50.000 + 100.000 = 3.150.000 gr</p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><strong>semoga</strong><strong> </strong><strong>membantu</strong><strong> </strong>dan maaf kalo salah </p><br />
